snippet.title: 502's Arcade Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
502's Arcade is a collection of fast paced arcade games. Ghost hunting in an procedural dungeon crawler, fast reflex puzzle solving in a potion shop, blasting through alien enemies and more games to come!

Coming next year to Steam and Nintendo Switch!

You can wishlist the game on Steam now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1781730?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=announcement
